get your Power Platform environment URL

Sign in to Power Apps.

Click the gear icon (⚙️) in the top-right corner.

Select Developer resources.

A panel will open showing:

Environment ID
Web API endpoint

Use the Web API Endpoint
If you see something like https://orgxxxx.api.crm.dynamics.com/api/data/v9.2/, then your Environment URL is simply:

https://orgxxxx.crm.dynamics.com
